{"tid":242120,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"返左三年7-11 你問我答","createTime":"2017-05-13T16:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T18:50:19.000Z","uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe3bb6bac0c397526c954fd40793d3dc259798b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"返無熱賣點既鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc24765d93dd092464e361ecbec3cf7e01593d","tid":242120,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"人工？？"},{"pid":"b45d534de52ee2612fa84d5a9994b4d9f4aa7b1e","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工？？</blockquote><br />\n40-50<br />\n準確數答唔到你<br />\n間間鋪唔同人工好易起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27dc2441ff5545a2679cd48423ce355d5e0ded4","tid":242120,"uid":76883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"有冇翻過夜更？"},{"pid":"8ebc917e21b52d7d39bc628552902e30c728eac3","tid":242120,"uid":66645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔問啦 驚自爆"},{"pid":"7e4b705208f8c38d7a0a5ca020867d9345e80585","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇翻過夜更？</blockquote><br />\n我間鋪唔開24<br />\n我多數返晏就到收鋪"},{"pid":"8b0bfc9e49bfedfd0dc104a53e14f84317d51cf2","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔問啦 驚自爆</blockquote><br />\n連登俾人起底會俾人笑樣衰<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"74dd20804adcc551480027e03a3ab5f231ec8bb2","tid":242120,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"經理好唔好人？<br />\n面對住啲閪客時，你會點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做過3個月多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96bdaaf004595ce58ab6ca48a6e125129989729","tid":242120,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:00:08.000Z","msg":"無諗過搵多D?"},{"pid":"574b8ccef43fb53f80ec8cce400982f186b8add8","tid":242120,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"醫院舖？"},{"pid":"96299b1d917c1e124592e6f236f6cbecfc664000","tid":242120,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"有冇抽小熊維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629f8fd1e11656af501907d1d319fa30bec0d27f","tid":242120,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"有冇後悔冇讀書?"},{"pid":"4f777dab6172fa1f619762b0e13db897f6aecd4c","tid":242120,"uid":76883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"有冇試過找錯錢或者收錯錢？"},{"pid":"5af38fb4ec7f918472725296f20f707b5f4814be","tid":242120,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"Hea唔hea? 得閒可以玩下手機？"},{"pid":"ddabc72dc414cf8b21f2abe979bd9d12e834821b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經理好唔好人？<br />\n面對住啲閪客時，你會點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做過3個月多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經理好人<br />\n因為間鋪都唔係佢既<br />\n之不過有時佢好人到要踩朝早六點踩到夜晚9點見到都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-<br />\n閪客黎講 都有好多種 是但講一次深刻經歷<br />\n7-11以前交費係可以就咁講低帳單number就幫你交到<br />\n依家一定要barcode qrcode <br />\n就係轉實行呢個做法嗰排<br />\n有個客黎話死都一定俾number就交到<br />\n我地同事都係咁講已經轉左要用barcode/qrcode先交到帳單 得number幫唔到你<br />\n但個客好撚硬頸 講左十五分鐘係到loop埋啲一定交到之類既野<br />\n最後我唔耐煩同佢講 <br />\n<br />\n小姐 我地都係跟公司指引做野 如果你繼續要係到無理取鬧落去 我唯有報警處理 因為你已經阻住我地做生意 如果你都係覺得我係專登唔幫你服務既 可以上寫字樓投訴我<br />\n<br />\n之類既野<br />\n最後條女嬲嬲地走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbe56e732a398c271a61ae39962434bbffc02dd","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無諗過搵多D?</blockquote><br />\n讀書時期PT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長工不了<br />\n但講多少少<br />\n7-11係即使做到分區經理<br />\n人工都好似係唔過20k <br />\n姐係得個名好聽only"},{"pid":"ee95db904dfdb6f2f0928acfb1fe271d304a446b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫院舖？</blockquote><br />\n地鐵鋪"},{"pid":"5642a74daeab2b650c1ca7146ae4c7e6f6c4a92e","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇抽小熊維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81804271b430774a127d960f52b0b8e68936707b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇後悔冇讀書?</blockquote><br />\n讀書時期PT JOB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家準備搵出路"},{"pid":"b91ac97ac5e38f8b53aebbe16b17f6e7d2b7b47b","tid":242120,"uid":66656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫院舖？</blockquote><br />\n醫院24架"},{"pid":"9a2fa8b5b83012ae970255f0c6bc92c6bcda72a0","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過找錯錢或者收錯錢？</blockquote><br />\n做左三年 淨係試過找多100俾人 一次<br />\n但經理好人唔洗賠<br />\n平時收工埋數都係加減0-20<br />\nBtw 公司指引係收工埋數差額多過十蚊就要賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講多少少 有同事試過幫人交帳單禁多左個0<br />\n最黎出糧出少左1000幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdc7b46933e3f2177304f093bd225c0e7de4c2b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hea唔hea? 得閒可以玩下手機？</blockquote><br />\n唔hea 返地鐵鋪人流多<br />\n收工時間一開始就keep住每個鐘做around 250單生意<br />\n<br />\n玩手機既野就 如果你做得柒又玩就俾人屌硬<br />\n我表現ok 得閒禁下無人屌<br />\n但基本上分區經理落黎睇閉仔都會屌人玩手機<br />\n利申我無理到照玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a7d1698d9d59a2ee0c0e9320c49656d8ae427b","tid":242120,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫院舖？</blockquote><br />\n醫院24架</blockquote><br />\n話說公司指引要員工每次埋單後講 多謝哂下次見<br />\n醫院鋪就一定唔可以講 要講多謝哂 byebye <br />\n呢啲位都做得幾貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5636bfc82e153a97f372dd4a5bc9d6e6ed664192","tid":242120,"uid":81508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醫院舖？</blockquote><br />\n醫院24架</blockquote><br />\n話說公司指引要員工每次埋單後講 多謝哂下次見<br />\n醫院鋪就一定唔可以講 要講多謝哂 byebye <br />\n呢啲位都做得幾貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}